<pre>Bankgiro-Inbetalningar
==============================================
This module is a Bankgiro Inbetalningar parser where [BG6040] [1] is the specification behind the code. PHP 5.3.10 was used.

Usage
-----
```php
$parser = new \BGI\BgiFileParser();
$parser->parseFile($file);
```
Testing
-------
Tests were conducted with PHPUnit 3.7.21.

Testfiles needed to conduct the tests are:
* [BgMaxfil1] [2]
* [BgMaxfil2] [3]
* [BgMaxfil3] [4]
* [BgMaxfil4] [5]
* [BgMaxfil5] [6]
and they should be placed in Tests/Files folder.

Some of the test files are not complying to the given standard and this has been reported to BGC several times, but nothing is corrected as 2013-07-02.
<b>Problems</b>
* In [BgMaxfil4] [5] row 18 is one char to long (81 instead of 80), remove the 
	last space to make the tests comply.
* Some transactions (in, [BgMaxfil3] [4], [BgMaxfil4] [5] and [BgMaxfil5] [6])
	with multiple references has a comma as delimiter. This is not given 
	explicit in [BG6040] [1]. The implementation takes care of that.

